data.description: This stunning single-story layout features a bright, open-concept living space. The kitchen is at the heart of the home and is a show-stopper! With high-end creamy ember cabinets, speckled granite, taupe subway tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances plus gas cooking! There is even a separate coffee bar or wine station, perfect for entertaining.    Enjoy dinner at the large island countertop or in the separate dining room.  The floors are beautiful with cinnamon walnut vinyl, an upgraded carpet, and a thicker pad for comfort.  Relax in the large primary suite with a large walk-in shower, double vanity and huge closet.  The covered back patio provides tons of shade and so will the 3 oak trees planted in the back. Best of all this home has paid off SOLAR PANELS!! The Electric bills are less than $50 a month so you will save thousands of dollars on utility bills! The buyer would assume the existing loan at only $100 a month with a 2% interest rate. So much better than paying $300 or more in utility bills every month!!  This home also has a water softener and sprinkler system. Prescott Oaks is located just west of Loop 1604 on Galm Road in the award-winning Northside ISD and this community offers great amenities!
